nodes.text: Jibuto was an ancient city located on the arid planet of Rajtiri. It was believed Jibuto prospered as a result of Rajtiri birthing and fostering more smugglers anywhere outside of Hutt Space. The city was known for its elaborate mausoleums as large as mansions, constructed for fathers, mothers, sons and daughters who had died in the line of unlawful duty and were hailed as heroes.
